When I was young,

598
00:28:35,510 --> 00:28:36,440
my skills were

599
00:28:36,530 --> 00:28:37,050
absolutely amazing.

600
00:28:37,050 --> 00:28:38,070
Alright, alright.

601
00:28:38,070 --> 00:28:38,810
Don't listen to your Second Aunt.

602
00:28:38,810 --> 00:28:39,770
She's just bragging.

603
00:28:39,770 --> 00:28:41,630
Heroes don't brag about the past.

604
00:28:41,880 --> 00:28:42,940
How am I bragging?

605
00:28:43,500 --> 00:28:44,160
Come here.

606
00:28:44,570 --> 00:28:45,500
Let's spar.

607
00:28:45,590 --> 00:28:46,680
Face your age.

608
00:28:47,790 --> 00:28:49,110
Forget fighting.

609
00:28:49,220 --> 00:28:49,980
In two years,

610
00:28:50,070 --> 00:28:50,700
just sneezing

611
00:28:50,700 --> 00:28:52,100
will throw your back out.

612
00:28:53,180 --> 00:28:54,440
You're exaggerating.

613
00:28:54,460 --> 00:28:55,380
Just you wait.

614
00:28:57,640 --> 00:28:58,640
Where's your dad?

615
00:29:00,160 --> 00:29:00,820
Over there.

616
00:29:01,160 --> 00:29:02,090
Waiting for you to come back

617
00:29:02,090 --> 00:29:03,020
to set the table.

618
00:29:10,740 --> 00:29:11,330
Lingling, Wenyuan,

619
00:29:11,330 --> 00:29:12,180
help me up.

620
00:29:13,510 --> 00:29:14,810
Be careful,

621
00:29:14,940 --> 00:29:16,340
don't hurt my back again.

622
00:29:19,550 --> 00:29:20,050
Okay.

623
00:29:58,160 --> 00:29:59,090
Wash your hands.

624
00:29:59,090 --> 00:30:00,180
We're eating soon.

625
00:30:01,900 --> 00:30:03,030
Where are you going?

626
00:30:03,070 --> 00:30:03,790
Outside.

627
00:30:04,330 --> 00:30:05,530
Where exactly?

628
00:30:05,920 --> 00:30:07,320
Outside is just outside.

629
00:30:07,350 --> 00:30:08,660
Where else?

630
00:30:09,050 --> 00:30:10,460
Slow down, Second Aunt.

631
00:30:10,550 --> 00:30:12,010
Yeah, I know.

632
00:30:17,570 --> 00:30:19,500
You think your Second Aunt is cool?

633
00:30:22,610 --> 00:30:24,240
Wash your hands. We're eating soon.

634
00:30:24,240 --> 00:30:24,940
Okay.

635
00:30:25,030 --> 00:30:25,550
Wash up.

636
00:30:34,750 --> 00:30:35,420
Let's go.

637
00:30:36,250 --> 00:30:36,780
Let's go.

638
00:30:39,030 --> 00:30:39,960
What's going on?

639
00:30:39,960 --> 00:30:40,500
Let's go.

640
00:30:40,940 --> 00:30:41,350
I...

641
00:30:41,460 --> 00:30:43,030
Your colleague came to deliver the sheep,

642
00:30:43,030 --> 00:30:44,290
and I just ran into him.

643
00:30:44,850 --> 00:30:45,750
I'm asking you.

644
00:30:47,720 --> 00:30:49,250
This housewarming gift...

645
00:30:49,720 --> 00:30:50,310
Lingling loves it.

646
00:30:50,310 --> 00:30:52,710
I ordered it specially a couple of days ago.

647
00:30:59,270 --> 00:31:00,810
Dad is unbelievable.

648
00:31:01,090 --> 00:31:03,020
He left without even taking a bite.

649
00:31:03,960 --> 00:31:04,900
I feel like his hair

650
00:31:04,900 --> 00:31:06,140
is getting thinner.

651
00:31:07,570 --> 00:31:08,970
Grandma, did you notice?

652
00:31:12,200 --> 00:31:13,660
Your dad is busy with work.

653
00:31:13,740 --> 00:31:15,000
He stays up late often.

654
00:31:15,350 --> 00:31:16,610
It's from exhaustion.

655
00:31:27,810 --> 00:31:28,880
I found a table.

656
00:31:29,680 --> 00:31:30,680
Here, put it here.

657
00:31:35,590 --> 00:31:36,240
Ju,

658
00:31:36,660 --> 00:31:37,850
you were thoughtful enough to buy this sheep,

659
00:31:37,850 --> 00:31:39,000
but why didn't you ask Yunfei

660
00:31:39,000 --> 00:31:40,060
to stay for dinner?

661
00:31:40,200 --> 00:31:40,660
He came all the way

662
00:31:40,660 --> 00:31:42,320
from the provincial capital.

663
00:31:44,960 --> 00:31:47,030
I haven't settled the score with you yet.

664
00:31:47,030 --> 00:31:47,740
Did you tell him

665
00:31:47,740 --> 00:31:49,200
that we were moving today?

666
00:31:50,110 --> 00:31:51,070
I've noticed something about you.

667
00:31:51,070 --> 00:31:51,610
Why do you always

668
00:31:51,610 --> 00:31:52,810
side with outsiders?

669
00:31:53,400 --> 00:31:54,500
That's enough, you two.

670
00:31:54,500 --> 00:31:55,440
Look at him pretending.

671
00:31:55,440 --> 00:31:56,530
I barely touched him.

672
00:31:56,530 --> 00:31:57,460
I'm not pretending.

673
00:31:57,460 --> 00:31:58,400
I moved stuff all afternoon.

674
00:31:58,400 --> 00:32:00,130
It hurts even when I don't move.

675
00:32:00,610 --> 00:32:02,310
No matter what,

676
00:32:02,420 --> 00:32:03,550
Yunfei is like a brother to me.

677
00:32:03,550 --> 00:32:04,810
How is he an outsider?

678
00:32:05,570 --> 00:32:07,030
I'm your real brother.

679
00:32:08,590 --> 00:32:10,720
I've been divorced from him for years.

680
00:32:11,220 --> 00:32:11,480
From now on,

681
00:32:11,480 --> 00:32:13,410
stop involving him in everything.

682
00:32:13,460 --> 00:32:14,790
Hurry up and get to work.

683
00:32:16,420 --> 00:32:17,460
Get to work.

684
00:32:18,830 --> 00:32:19,490
Get to work.

685
00:32:30,160 --> 00:32:30,530
Look.

686
00:32:31,550 --> 00:32:32,950
Why are you looking at me?

687
00:32:33,310 --> 00:32:33,700
Aren't you

688
00:32:33,700 --> 00:32:35,230
quite experienced in this?

689
00:32:35,610 --> 00:32:36,610
What experience?

690
00:32:37,240 --> 00:32:38,100
Back in the day,

691
00:32:38,380 --> 00:32:39,200
in one night,

692
00:32:39,310 --> 00:32:40,910
you could skin so many pelts.

693
00:32:41,830 --> 00:32:42,310
That...

694
00:32:42,440 --> 00:32:43,720
That was over ten years ago.

695
00:32:43,720 --> 00:32:45,380
Why do you keep bringing it up?

696
00:32:47,700 --> 00:32:48,270
Fine.

697
00:32:48,700 --> 00:32:50,030
Guo, go find Yan.

698
00:32:50,140 --> 00:32:51,000
Let her do it.

699
00:32:51,270 --> 00:32:51,880
She knows how to use a knife.

700
00:32:51,880 --> 00:32:52,270
Okay.

701
00:32:52,530 --> 00:32:52,990
I'll go.

702
00:32:53,220 --> 00:32:54,030
I'll go find her.

703
00:32:54,030 --> 00:32:55,070
Okay.

704
00:32:55,960 --> 00:32:56,980
I'll butcher it. I'll do it.

705
00:32:56,980 --> 00:32:58,780
You don't need to worry about it.

706
00:33:00,700 --> 00:33:01,830
Go ahead. I'll do it.

707
00:33:02,750 --> 00:33:03,050
Don't worry about it.

708
00:33:03,050 --> 00:33:03,700
Go.

709
00:33:03,790 --> 00:33:04,610
Do a good job.

710
00:33:07,460 --> 00:33:08,050
My back...

711
00:33:08,050 --> 00:33:08,850
I'll help you.

712
00:33:09,570 --> 00:33:10,000
Here, here, here.

713
00:33:10,000 --> 00:33:11,130
Just follow my hand.

714
00:33:11,480 --> 00:33:11,960
Sit down.

715
00:33:11,960 --> 00:33:13,220
I'll give it a good rub.

716
00:33:13,240 --> 00:33:14,570
Right here. Right here.

717
00:33:20,200 --> 00:33:20,810
How is it?

718
00:33:22,090 --> 00:33:22,700
Better?

719
00:33:23,810 --> 00:33:25,470
Why are you back so late today?

720
00:33:26,570 --> 00:33:28,370
I chatted with Mr. Meng for a bit.

721
00:33:29,090 --> 00:33:31,550
The mine is having inspections and layoffs.

722
00:33:31,770 --> 00:33:32,810
It's a total mess.

723
00:33:34,680 --> 00:33:35,920
Layoffs at work...

724
00:33:36,000 --> 00:33:37,200
You should talk less.

725
00:33:37,640 --> 00:33:38,270
Things like this

726
00:33:38,270 --> 00:33:39,900
are the easiest way to offend people.

727
00:33:39,900 --> 00:33:40,750
If you're not careful,

728
00:33:40,750 --> 00:33:41,590
both the higher-ups and those below

729
00:33:41,590 --> 00:33:43,190
will have a problem with you.

730
00:33:46,460 --> 00:33:47,250
Quite a few

731
00:33:47,480 --> 00:33:48,480
old comrades who came with me

732
00:33:48,480 --> 00:33:49,540
from the salt field

733
00:33:50,310 --> 00:33:51,530
are at this age.

734
00:33:51,940 --> 00:33:53,160
If they really get laid off,

735
00:33:53,160 --> 00:33:54,820
finding a new job will be hard.

736
00:33:56,590 --> 00:33:58,190
If they look around for help,

737
00:33:58,330 --> 00:33:59,790
it'll still be my problem.

738
00:34:03,400 --> 00:34:04,460
To be honest,

739
00:34:04,770 --> 00:34:06,240
that report by Shao Yunfei

740
00:34:06,720 --> 00:34:07,880
had a big impact.

741
00:34:08,190 --> 00:34:09,280
It made the city leaders

742
00:34:09,280 --> 00:34:10,340
and us at Xinhai

743
00:34:10,460 --> 00:34:11,480
all very nervous.

744
00:34:13,460 --> 00:34:14,090
Why don't you...

745
00:34:14,090 --> 00:34:15,750
I'm not going to say anything.

746
00:34:15,960 --> 00:34:18,290
If you want to say something, you go ahead.

747
00:34:18,650 --> 00:34:19,510
Sis.

748
00:34:20,570 --> 00:34:21,230
What's wrong?

749
00:34:21,230 --> 00:34:22,260
Come look, quick.

750
00:34:22,960 --> 00:34:23,760
What happened?

751
00:34:23,760 --> 00:34:24,500
Slow down.

752
00:34:25,280 --> 00:34:25,840
Slow down.

753
00:34:25,840 --> 00:34:26,639
What's wrong?

754
00:34:29,150 --> 00:34:30,350
Look at this stomach.

755
00:34:30,650 --> 00:34:31,980
It's full of coal slag.

756
00:34:32,050 --> 00:34:33,580
Can we still eat this sheep?

757
00:34:43,010 --> 00:34:44,300
Don't eat the tripe.

758
00:34:48,690 --> 00:34:49,840
Congratulations on the new house, Mom.

759
00:34:49,840 --> 00:34:50,230
Come on.

760
00:34:50,230 --> 00:34:51,070
Come on.

761
00:34:51,630 --> 00:34:52,280
Cheers.

762
00:34:52,360 --> 00:34:53,820
Happy housewarming, Mom.

763
00:35:00,260 --> 00:35:00,920
Drink less.

764
00:35:01,000 --> 00:35:02,400
Eat more veggies, Lingling.

765
00:35:02,400 --> 00:35:03,530
Don't just eat meat.

766
00:35:04,500 --> 00:35:05,030
How about

767
00:35:05,070 --> 00:35:05,880
I call the kitchen in a bit,

768
00:35:05,880 --> 00:35:06,650
and tell them

769
00:35:06,730 --> 00:35:07,730
to take that sheep

770
00:35:08,190 --> 00:35:09,720
straight to my restaurant?

771
00:35:11,070 --> 00:35:12,330
Are you President Bai?

772
00:35:12,780 --> 00:35:14,510
Or are you becoming President Black-hearted?

773
00:35:14,510 --> 00:35:15,920
How can you be so shady?

774
00:35:16,010 --> 00:35:17,000
Food our family won't eat,

775
00:35:17,000 --> 00:35:18,360
you want to feed to others?

776
00:35:18,360 --> 00:35:19,780
Inside that sheep's stomach,

777
00:35:19,780 --> 00:35:20,840
it's all coal dust.

778
00:35:21,110 --> 00:35:22,860
The heavy metal content is high.

779
00:35:22,860 --> 00:35:24,480
Wrap it up and throw it far away.

780
00:35:24,480 --> 00:35:26,070
Don't let anyone pick it up and eat it.

781
00:35:26,070 --> 00:35:26,670
I know.

782
00:35:27,460 --> 00:35:28,320
Around Tianduo,

783
00:35:28,320 --> 00:35:29,460
there are so many mines.

784
00:35:29,460 --> 00:35:30,320
What's blowing in the wind

785
00:35:30,320 --> 00:35:31,900
is practically all coal dust.

786
00:35:31,900 --> 00:35:33,830
Lamb prices have gone up recently.

787
00:35:34,110 --> 00:35:35,130
The lamb in our restaurant

788
00:35:35,130 --> 00:35:36,930
is all imported from out of town.

789
00:35:37,500 --> 00:35:38,700
Here, have some Coke.

790
00:35:39,590 --> 00:35:40,190
It's cold.

791
00:35:42,920 --> 00:35:44,690
Some small coal mines these days

792
00:35:44,690 --> 00:35:46,020
are really outrageous.

793
00:35:46,030 --> 00:35:47,210
They don't do any dust suppression.

794
00:35:47,210 --> 00:35:48,230
They bought sprinkler trucks,

795
00:35:48,230 --> 00:35:48,960
but they just sit there

796
00:35:48,960 --> 00:35:49,940
unused.

797
00:35:50,030 --> 00:35:50,690
Since they bought them,

798
00:35:50,690 --> 00:35:51,500
why not use them?

799
00:35:51,500 --> 00:35:52,840
To deal with inspections.

800
00:35:52,840 --> 00:35:53,650
When inspectors come,

801
00:35:53,650 --> 00:35:54,300
they fill them up,

802
00:35:54,300 --> 00:35:54,900
drive them out,

803
00:35:54,900 --> 00:35:55,830
and put on a show.

804
00:35:56,650 --> 00:35:57,480
If you ask me,

805
00:35:57,920 --> 00:35:58,670
we should take those

806
00:35:58,670 --> 00:36:00,130
non-compliant small coal mines

807
00:36:00,130 --> 00:36:01,390
and shut them all down.

808
00:36:03,090 --> 00:36:04,350
That's not realistic.

809
00:36:04,460 --> 00:36:05,150
Think about a mine.

810
00:36:05,150 --> 00:36:06,650
How many people depend on it for a living?

811
00:36:06,650 --> 00:36:08,180
You can't just shut it down.

812
00:36:08,590 --> 00:36:09,360
If you ask me,

813
00:36:09,460 --> 00:36:11,520
my sister isn't cut out to be a leader.

814
00:36:11,590 --> 00:36:12,500
As for being a captain,

815
00:36:12,500 --> 00:36:13,690
she can only be a deputy.

816
00:36:13,690 --> 00:36:15,340
Her view is too one-sided.

817
00:36:15,920 --> 00:36:17,110
The seven coal mines in our city

818
00:36:17,110 --> 00:36:18,840
were all introduced by Uncle Lin.

819
00:36:18,840 --> 00:36:19,550
Our development these years

820
00:36:19,550 --> 00:36:20,340
relied entirely on them.

821
00:36:20,340 --> 00:36:22,070
How can she just shut them down?

822
00:36:22,840 --> 00:36:23,210
Mom.

823
00:36:23,780 --> 00:36:24,170
Here.

824
00:36:28,610 --> 00:36:30,480
Environmental awareness has improved,

825
00:36:30,480 --> 00:36:31,680
which is a good thing.

826
00:36:32,670 --> 00:36:33,530
But some people

827
00:36:33,860 --> 00:36:35,050
tend to overcorrect.

828
00:36:35,050 --> 00:36:36,420
They only see one side,

829
00:36:36,510 --> 00:36:37,730
or even just a corner,

830
00:36:37,840 --> 00:36:39,170
and start making a fuss.

831
00:36:39,710 --> 00:36:40,610
These sheep,

832
00:36:40,710 --> 00:36:42,190
if those people saw them,

833
00:36:42,570 --> 00:36:43,300
they'd say

834
00:36:43,400 --> 00:36:44,420
economic development

835
00:36:44,420 --> 00:36:46,220
is destroying the environment.

836
00:36:54,230 --> 00:36:55,130
Enough talk.

837
00:36:55,230 --> 00:36:56,050
Let's eat.

838
00:36:59,500 --> 00:37:00,360
Bai Ju,

839
00:37:00,460 --> 00:37:01,190
eat more.

840
00:37:01,730 --> 00:37:01,960
I am.

841
00:37:01,960 --> 00:37:03,490
Have some veggies, you two.

842
00:37:12,690 --> 00:37:13,210
Captain Bai,

843
00:37:13,210 --> 00:37:13,780
yours.

844
00:37:17,820 --> 00:37:18,880
What's that smell?

845
00:37:18,920 --> 00:37:19,650
It stinks.

846
00:37:20,170 --> 00:37:21,630
Someone threw stuff at me.

847
00:37:24,590 --> 00:37:26,280
What happened? Assaulting a police officer?

848
00:37:26,280 --> 00:37:27,030
Not exactly.

849
00:37:27,110 --> 00:37:28,610
It was just chaotic.

850
00:37:28,710 --> 00:37:29,340
Coal dust,

851
00:37:29,440 --> 00:37:30,170
sheep intestines, tripe...

852
00:37:30,170 --> 00:37:30,840
they threw everything.

853
00:37:30,840 --> 00:37:31,860
Got it all over me.

854
00:37:31,960 --> 00:37:33,560
No wonder it smells so gamey.

855
00:37:33,800 --> 00:37:34,320
After work,

856
00:37:34,320 --> 00:37:35,320
wash up properly.

857
00:37:36,300 --> 00:37:38,100
This isn't the first time, is it?

858
00:37:38,570 --> 00:37:40,170
You're involved every time.

859
00:37:40,320 --> 00:37:41,280
And every time, you're leading

860
00:37:41,280 --> 00:37:42,480
different herdsmen.

861
00:37:43,500 --> 00:37:44,510
Why are you blocking

862
00:37:44,510 --> 00:37:46,170
the entrance to the coal mine?

863
00:37:46,400 --> 00:37:47,460
If you have demands,

864
00:37:47,460 --> 00:37:48,090
express them through

865
00:37:48,090 --> 00:37:49,460
official channels.

866
00:37:50,920 --> 00:37:52,170
What you're doing now

867
00:37:52,460 --> 00:37:53,210
violates the

868
00:37:53,340 --> 00:37:55,280
Public Security Administration Punishments Law.

869
00:37:55,280 --> 00:37:57,150
Interfering with the company's normal production.

870
00:37:57,150 --> 00:37:57,920
Besides,

871
00:37:58,210 --> 00:37:59,470
none of these pastures

872
00:37:59,590 --> 00:38:00,320
seem to belong

873
00:38:00,320 --> 00:38:01,280
to your family.

874
00:38:02,000 --> 00:38:03,650
Your demand is

875
00:38:03,760 --> 00:38:05,690
for them to stop mining.

876
00:38:05,940 --> 00:38:06,380
You...

877
00:38:06,780 --> 00:38:07,670
This demand... Captain,

878
00:38:07,670 --> 00:38:08,860
isn't it too extreme?

879
00:38:08,860 --> 00:38:09,590
Just in time.

880
00:38:09,630 --> 00:38:10,890
I'll leave this to you.

881
00:38:11,940 --> 00:38:12,870
What's going on?

882
00:38:20,920 --> 00:38:21,730
Han,

883
00:38:21,840 --> 00:38:23,100
do you know each other?

884
00:38:28,260 --> 00:38:28,980
No.

885
00:38:32,820 --> 00:38:34,440
Then you... you have to recuse yourself.

886
00:38:34,440 --> 00:38:36,010
She does have to recuse herself.

887
00:38:36,010 --> 00:38:37,610
The one I hit is her relative.

888
00:38:40,030 --> 00:38:41,010
Who did you hit?

889
00:38:44,760 --> 00:38:45,780
Does it hurt?

890
00:38:46,110 --> 00:38:47,210
Yes.

891
00:38:49,550 --> 00:38:51,010
Why don't you go somewhere

892
00:38:51,130 --> 00:38:52,170
and get a couple of stitches?

893
00:38:52,170 --> 00:38:52,920
Go to whom?

894
00:38:53,440 --> 00:38:54,500
Have Mom stitch it?

895
00:38:55,170 --> 00:38:55,880
It's fine.

896
00:38:57,940 --> 00:39:00,070
That Han Xuechao really is something.

897
00:39:00,300 --> 00:39:01,800
He's too heavy-handed.

898
00:39:01,900 --> 00:39:02,800
It's a minor injury.

899
00:39:02,800 --> 00:39:04,060
He'll get over it soon.

900
00:39:04,550 --> 00:39:05,410
It was chaotic.

901
00:39:05,500 --> 00:39:06,590
He didn't mean it.

902
00:39:07,110 --> 00:39:09,040
Maybe he didn't even recognize me.

903
00:39:10,820 --> 00:39:12,360
Brother, thank you.

904
00:39:15,650 --> 00:39:17,090
You choose to settle.

905
00:39:17,210 --> 00:39:18,780
According to the 'Public Security Administration Punishments Law',

906
00:39:18,780 --> 00:39:19,590
he'll be fined 200 yuan,

907
00:39:19,590 --> 00:39:21,190
and that will be the end of it.

908
00:39:21,500 --> 00:39:23,830
It's a good thing the person he hit was you.

909
00:39:24,980 --> 00:39:25,960
That last part

910
00:39:26,320 --> 00:39:27,920
sounds so weird.

911
00:39:40,530 --> 00:39:41,500
I have things to do.

912
00:39:41,500 --> 00:39:42,430
I'm leaving now.

913
00:39:42,900 --> 00:39:43,980
Take care of your hand.

914
00:39:43,980 --> 00:39:44,380
Okay.

915
00:39:44,980 --> 00:39:45,610
Han.

916
00:39:48,000 --> 00:39:48,650
Han.

917
00:39:54,900 --> 00:39:56,030
Don't do this again.

918
00:39:57,400 --> 00:39:59,320
If it's classified as picking quarrels and provoking trouble,

919
00:39:59,320 --> 00:40:00,110
it won't be as simple

920
00:40:00,110 --> 00:40:01,040
as paying a fine.

921
00:40:01,480 --> 00:40:02,840
You'll be detained.

922
00:40:03,440 --> 00:40:04,500
Let them detain me.

923
00:40:04,800 --> 00:40:05,660
I'm not afraid.

924
00:40:06,090 --> 00:40:08,380
It's not like I haven't been in there before.

925
00:40:08,380 --> 00:40:09,380
Even going to jail

926
00:40:10,230 --> 00:40:12,030
is better than being an ingrate.

927
00:40:12,570 --> 00:40:13,000
Han Xuechao,

928
00:40:13,000 --> 00:40:14,330
what do you mean by that?

929
00:40:16,150 --> 00:40:17,260
You know exactly

930
00:40:17,360 --> 00:40:18,000
what you did.

931
00:40:18,000 --> 00:40:18,730
What did I do?

932
00:40:21,630 --> 00:40:22,110
Yeah.

933
00:40:23,150 --> 00:40:24,030
What did you do?

934
00:40:25,030 --> 00:40:26,210
What did our Mountain Patrol

935
00:40:26,210 --> 00:40:27,010
do in the past?

936
00:40:27,010 --> 00:40:28,380
And what are you doing now

937
00:40:28,380 --> 00:40:29,440
in that police uniform?

938
00:40:29,440 --> 00:40:30,840
You speak for your brother,

939
00:40:30,840 --> 00:40:32,240
for the coal mine people,

940
00:40:32,290 --> 00:40:33,260
and fine us.

941
00:40:33,550 --> 00:40:34,750
I'm a police officer.

942
00:40:35,420 --> 00:40:36,630
I'm doing my job.

943
00:40:38,030 --> 00:40:38,670
You're worse than me,

944
00:40:38,670 --> 00:40:40,200
a guy in a security uniform.

945
00:40:40,800 --> 00:40:41,320
Hello?

946
00:40:42,530 --> 00:40:43,590
I'll be right back.

947
00:40:44,570 --> 00:40:45,260
Fired?

948
00:40:45,780 --> 00:40:46,980
Why are you firing me?

949
00:40:47,650 --> 00:40:48,360
When I came out,

950
00:40:48,360 --> 00:40:49,190
I asked the supervisor for leave.

951
00:40:49,190 --> 00:40:50,390
You know that, right?

952
00:40:50,420 --> 00:40:51,750
So what if I hit someone?

953
00:40:51,880 --> 00:40:52,680
I hit a bad guy.

954
00:40:52,730 --> 00:40:53,610
You know that, right?

955
00:40:53,610 --> 00:40:53,980
I...

956
00:41:25,610 --> 00:41:26,280
Eat up.

957
00:41:26,900 --> 00:41:28,760
I didn't put meat in your noodles.

958
00:41:36,090 --> 00:41:36,650
If you want to

959
00:41:36,650 --> 00:41:38,130
find a more stable job,

960
00:41:39,400 --> 00:41:40,280
I can ask around for you.

961
00:41:40,280 --> 00:41:40,980
No need.

962
00:41:41,090 --> 00:41:42,290
I'm not finished yet.

963
00:41:42,400 --> 00:41:44,130
I know what you're going to say.

964
00:41:44,420 --> 00:41:46,080
Isn't it just going to the mine

965
00:41:46,230 --> 00:41:47,230
and working for Bai Chun?

966
00:41:47,230 --> 00:41:49,430
Working is better than hitting people.

967
00:41:58,280 --> 00:42:00,280
Xinhai Group has offices and hotels

968
00:42:00,650 --> 00:42:01,550
in the city.

969
00:42:02,900 --> 00:42:03,710
You could be a security guard

970
00:42:03,710 --> 00:42:04,510
or something.

971
00:42:05,800 --> 00:42:07,060
Is there a difference?

972
00:42:08,880 --> 00:42:09,500
Without Xinhai,

973
00:42:09,500 --> 00:42:10,550
will I starve?

974
00:42:22,050 --> 00:42:22,880
Han Xuechao.

975
00:42:23,900 --> 00:42:26,780
You can't achieve environmental protection by protesting.

976
00:42:26,780 --> 00:42:27,480
I was just doing

977
00:42:27,480 --> 00:42:28,780
my job.

978
00:42:29,300 --> 00:42:30,170
Doing this

979
00:42:30,820 --> 00:42:32,400
won't do any good,

980
00:42:32,500 --> 00:42:34,030
and will only break the law.

981
00:42:34,530 --> 00:42:35,360
In the end, the company

982
00:42:35,360 --> 00:42:36,820
will just keep producing.

983
00:42:37,190 --> 00:42:38,610
You can't help those herdsmen,

984
00:42:38,610 --> 00:42:39,320
nor can you save the sheep

985
00:42:39,320 --> 00:42:40,400
that are sick or dead.

986
00:42:40,400 --> 00:42:41,150
You're just

987
00:42:41,260 --> 00:42:42,390
asking for trouble.

988
00:42:49,110 --> 00:42:50,510
I know what you're doing.

989
00:42:55,820 --> 00:42:58,820
But isn't that like looking for a needle
in a haystack?

990
00:42:59,780 --> 00:43:01,710
If the police can't find anything,

991
00:43:06,070 --> 00:43:07,230
what makes you think you can?
